## Dependencies and Installation Intructions:

Get networkred
    
    git clone https://github.com/nefan/networkred.git

Download the ssparse library

    git clone https://github.com/nefan/sparse.git

and follow the installation instructions in the package. 
Likewise with cljmex (for generating the MATLAB mex files):

    git clone https://github.com/nefan/sparse.git

Download and install KLU from http://www.suitesparse.com

...

Edit networkred_config.mk to have the correct paths, compiler flags, etc.
Then compile 

    make

and add lib/ to MATLAB's seach path or link with object files lib/*.o
